<H3> <TI>   Serbs Shell Zupanja; No Casualties Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serbs Shell Zupanja; No Casualties Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0306223594 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
2200 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0306223594 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 2025, chetniks from strongholds in the occupied 
areas of Bosnian Posavina launched a fresh attack on the town of 
Zupanja and the village of Bosnjaci. Several large-caliber 
shells caused fresh material damage, but no one was wounded. 
Chetniks also attacked the Zupanja Posavina area shortly before 
1300. They fired a dozen shells on Zupanja and Bosnjaci. 

</TEXT>

