<F P=102>   LD0706223694 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 2000 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0706223694 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The main hearing at the trial of Dusko Tomic, 
secretary-general of the 1st Children's Embassy, will begin on 
11 June, Bosnia-Herzegovina Press reports. It is suspected that 
Tomic has cooperated with the aggressor and he is considered the 
one most guilty for the inadequate organization of a convoy 
carrying food from Macedonia [Former Yugoslav Republic of 
Macedonia -- FYROM], which eventually ended up in the 
aggressor's hands in Pale. 

</TEXT>

