<F P=100> YUGOSLAVIA </F>
<F P=101> Kosovo </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Trumped-Up' Trial of 13 Albanians To Resume </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Trumped-Up' Trial of 13 Albanians To Resume </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0706183194 Tirana Radio Tirana Network in Albanian 1330 
GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0706183194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana Radio Tirana Network </F>
<F P=105>  Albanian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The trumped-up trial of the 13 Albanians who were 
charged with impersonating leaders of the Defense Ministry 
[words indistinct] of Kosova will resume on 20 June. The trial 
began on 18 April but was postponed because of complaints by the 
attorneys, who are demanding that the prosecutor and deputy 
prosecutor of the Serb Prosecution Office for the Prishtina 
region be removed from the trial. 
  The attorneys have confirmed that the trial will continue, 
even though a request for defense has not been approved. The 
attorneys of the accused have denied the charges and consider 
the trial to be a politically trumped-up one against the 
Albanians in Kosova. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-31319 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreeu110_y_94007" </HT>


